pageType: content
background:
  type: solid
  color: "$primary"
elements:
  - elementId: nav-label
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 24, 200, 22]
    content:
      style: "$caption"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>01 / Context &amp; Objective</p>
  - elementId: heading
    elementType: text
    bounds: [60, 60, 700, 42]
    content:
      style: "$heading"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Context &amp; Objective</strong></p>
  - elementId: accent-bar
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 112, 80, 4]
    shapeName: rect
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: context-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 140, 540, 200]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"
  - elementId: context-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 152, 500, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Context</strong></p>
  - elementId: context-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 186, 500, 150]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Roc4t has recruited two remote designers for AutoCAD and 3D work.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:8px">In parallel, we want to build an AI agent capable of performing the same tasks — <span style="color:$text;"><strong>better and faster</strong></span>.</p>
  - elementId: objective-card
    elementType: shape
    bounds: [60, 350, 540, 270]
    shapeName: roundRect
    adjustments: [8000]
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$surface"
    border:
      style: solid
      width: 1
      color: "$border"
  - elementId: objective-title
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 362, 500, 28]
    content:
      fontSize: 16
      color: "$accent"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p><strong>Objective</strong></p>
  - elementId: objective-body
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 398, 500, 210]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p>Build a unified production chain around:</p>
        <p style="margin-top:6px"><span style="color:$text;"><strong>AutoCAD</strong></span> + <span style="color:$text;"><strong>Revit/BIM</strong></span> + <span style="color:$text;"><strong>AI Agents</strong></span> + <span style="color:$text;"><strong>3D Immersive Review</strong></span></p>
        <p style="margin-top:12px">To produce faster with standardized outputs, reduce manual errors, and enable the lead to visualize and modify without touching technical tools.</p>
  - elementId: icon-autocad
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [700, 160, 48, 48]
    iconName: "fas:drafting-compass"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: icon-bim
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [700, 280, 48, 48]
    iconName: "fas:building"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: icon-ai
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [700, 400, 48, 48]
    iconName: "fas:robot"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: icon-3d
    elementType: icon
    bounds: [700, 520, 48, 48]
    iconName: "fas:cube"
    fill:
      type: solid
      color: "$accent"
  - elementId: label-autocad
    elementType: text
    bounds: [764, 164, 300, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>AutoCAD</p>
  - elementId: label-bim
    elementType: text
    bounds: [764, 284, 300, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>Revit / BIM</p>
  - elementId: label-ai
    elementType: text
    bounds: [764, 404, 300, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>AI Agents</p>
  - elementId: label-3d
    elementType: text
    bounds: [764, 524, 300, 40]
    content:
      fontSize: 18
      color: "$text"
      fontFamily: "Arial"
      align: [left, middle]
      wrap: false
      text: |
        <p>3D Immersive Review</p>
